<LanguageData>
  <!-- EN: gas mask -->
  <rxApparel_GasMask.label>防毒面具</rxApparel_GasMask.label>
  <!-- EN: A mask that protects the wearer from toxic gasses and other air-borne contaminants.\nThe filters wear out fairly quickly, so it's recommended to wear this only when necessary.\n\n<i><color=#66E0E4FF>Remote Tech (Continued)</color></i> -->
  <rxApparel_GasMask.description>可在有毒气体和其他气载污染物中保护穿戴者的面具。
过滤器的损耗相当快，所以推荐只在必要时穿戴。</rxApparel_GasMask.description>
  <!-- EN: portable remote detonator -->
  <rxApparel_PortableDetonator.label>便携式遥控起爆器</rxApparel_PortableDetonator.label>
  <!-- EN: A portable version of the detonator table for triggering remote explosives. Has limited range and runs on a non-rechargeable battery- but hey, you can almost fit it in your pocket. Almost.\nWorks only on channel 1, but can be upgraded once channels have been researched. Unequip to upgrade.\n\n<i><color=#66E0E4FF>Remote Tech (Continued)</color></i> -->
  <rxApparel_PortableDetonator.description>便携版的起爆器，用于触发远程炸药。范围有限，使用不可充电电池——但，几乎可以装进口袋。
  仅在频道1上工作，但可以在研究频道后升级。卸下装备以进行升级。</rxApparel_PortableDetonator.description>
  <!-- EN: Basic channels -->
  <rxApparel_PortableDetonator.comps.CompUpgrade.label>基础频道</rxApparel_PortableDetonator.comps.CompUpgrade.label>
  <!-- EN: Enables the detonator to trigger explosives on 3 separate channels. -->
  <rxApparel_PortableDetonator.comps.CompUpgrade.effectDescription>使起爆器能够在3个独立频道上触发炸药。</rxApparel_PortableDetonator.comps.CompUpgrade.effectDescription>
</LanguageData>
